INSERT [dbo].[Specs] ([ControId], [SpecificationlName], [Description], [Guidance]) VALUES ( 117, N'(1)', N'The organization employs redundant power cabling paths that are physically separated by [Assignment: organization-defined distance].', N'Physically separate, redundant power cables help to ensure that power continues to flow in the event one of the cables is cut or otherwise damaged.')
